{
  "stem": "20088.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody who was going direction Marseilles, it was going to Marseilles, so French prisoners of wars, and all Dutch, Belgium, French people, all were going on this boat.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the men were in the hold, but the women were in cabins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were four to a cabin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a Dutch girl called [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Kaya, ?] who I had met in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was coming in with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The fourth, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yes, I think it was-- that's another story, but, I mean, it's not my story.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's another woman who had come all the way from us-- with us from-- well, first from Holland, but then from Auschwitz, had done all this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was similar age to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she has had a daughter, who she had lost somewhere in Auschwitz, was separated and didn't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was always very sad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she said later on she was very jealous of-- that my mother was with me all the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she-- she joined with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so there were four of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we had still our Russian uniforms, but from the English or the New Zealanders, we got plimsolls to walk on deck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we-- well, we had it very good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We could sit outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was June.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was lovely, you know, lovely weather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was a fantastic journey through-- I mean, it's a luxury cruise that goes through from Odessa, through the Dardanelles, and the [INAUDIBLE], and Turkey, and then Greece, and Italy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first meal we had, we-- they called us to the dining room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was white table cloths, and silver-plated cutlery, and glasses, and wonderful, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- and we had sheets.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
